tool_description:
OneWinner.Me is a service that lets you check the earning expectation of your lottery numbers, and register your combination to prevent other players from choosing similar ones.

In lotteries (Euro Millions, …), some combinations are more played than others. It is better to choose combinations rarely played : they have the same probability of draw, but pay much more, because there are fewer winners.


The service works through a crowdsourcing technology, and advanced learning algorithms.

This API allows third party application to check and register combinations into the OneWinner.Me service. 

For the moment, only Euro Millions lottery is available, but more are coming soon. 

Good luck Mashapers, and enjoy !
name: OneWinner.Me
title: OneWinner.Me

api_list.name: RegisterEMComb
api_list.description:
This method will register a Euro Millions (EM) lottery combination. Registering a combination will prevent other players from choosing the same. 
Euro Millions is the biggest lottery in the worlds. This pan European lottery game is run in 10 countries at the same time. Approximately 20 million people play every week in Europe.
A Euro Millions combination is composed of 5 numbers and 2 stars.

required_parameters.name: star2
required_parameters.description: 2nd number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 11.

required_parameters.name: num1
required_parameters.description: 1st number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 50.

required_parameters.name: num2
required_parameters.description: 2nd number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 50.

required_parameters.name: num3
required_parameters.description: 3rd number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 50.

required_parameters.name: num4
required_parameters.description: 4th number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 50.

required_parameters.name: num5
required_parameters.description: 5th number of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 50.

required_parameters.name: star1
required_parameters.description: 1st star of the lottery combination you want to register. Between 1 and 11.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://onewinnerme-onewinnerme.p.rapidapi.com/registeremcomb/12/23/31/34/45/3/6"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "onewinnerme-onewinnerme.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: GetEMScore
api_list.description:

Euro Millions is the biggest lottery in the worlds. This pan European lottery game is run in 10 countries at the same time. Approximately 20 million people play every week in Europe.
